Package: bbs-server
Version: 0.4.1
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Jon Kirkpatrick <jon@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/JonKirkpatrick/bbs
Description: Build-a-Bot Stadium Server - Extensible bot arena platform
 Build-a-Bot Stadium is a contract-first, extensible bot-arena platform that
 orchestrates game execution and manages bot sessions via a JSON protocol.
 .
 Features:
  - Extensible plugin-based game system (Go, Python, Rust, etc.)
  - SQLite persistence for matches, profiles, and federation state
  - Web dashboard for arena management and live viewing
  - Process-based plugin architecture with RPC contract
  - Federation-ready with outbox/inbox patterns
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31)
Standards-Version: 4.6.1
Section: misc
Priority: optional
